AMMAN, April 7. /TASS/. Jordanian Foreign Minister Ayman Safadi will visit Moscow on April 16 in order to participate in the fifth Russian-Arab Cooperation Forum, Russian Foreign Minister Sergey Lavrov stated on the outcomes of the talks with Safadi.
“We have agreed to continue a close dialogue, and we do not part for long,” he noted. “On April 16, my colleague and my friend will participate in the fifth session of the Russian-Arab Forum at the ministerial level”.
